Test TCLLIBPATH separator fix
==============================

This test verifies that TCLLIBPATH uses space separators (as required by Tcl)
rather than colon separators (which are used by PATH, LD_LIBRARY_PATH, etc).

The test validates the logic pattern used in rip-environment.in and linuxcnc.in:
1. Tests the TCLLIBPATH appending logic with empty initial value
2. Tests the logic with pre-existing TCLLIBPATH values
3. Verifies that space separators are used, not colons

This ensures that the scripts will not break TCLLIBPATH when run multiple times.
